Chen Xiaoxi!

118
00:08:24,680 --> 00:08:25,680
Chen Xiaoxi!

119
00:08:27,120 --> 00:08:27,959
Where are you?

120
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:30,000
Chen Xiaoxi!

121
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:33,320
We all care about you!

122
00:08:35,360 --> 00:08:36,159
Chen Xiaoxi!

123
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:38,679
Come out!

124
00:08:44,320 --> 00:08:45,600
