125
00:09:14,240 --> 00:09:15,120
General...

126
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:17,279
Your father left this for you.

127
00:09:26,879 --> 00:09:29,440
Father, Mother.

128
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:32,240
Yan.

129
00:09:32,679 --> 00:09:35,320
I know it's hard to accept right away.

130
00:09:36,360 --> 00:09:38,120
General wouldn't want

131
00:09:38,639 --> 00:09:40,320
to see you like this.

132
00:09:46,759 --> 00:09:47,840
Did you find him?

