169
00:12:42,519 --> 00:12:43,919
Fight it to the end then.

170
00:12:45,759 --> 00:12:47,440
We can't choose how we're born,

171
00:12:47,799 --> 00:12:49,399
but we can shape our own lives.

172
00:12:52,440 --> 00:12:53,679
The Chen Xiaoxi I know

173
00:12:54,320 --> 00:12:57,480
has only been you.

174
00:12:58,799 --> 00:12:59,440
But...

175
00:13:01,480 --> 00:13:03,720
But I defied my father and killed him!

176
00:13:05,120 --> 00:13:05,799
So what?

177
00:13:06,919 --> 00:13:09,039
