189
00:13:38,240 --> 00:13:38,799
But...

190
00:13:39,320 --> 00:13:40,120
No buts.

191
00:13:41,679 --> 00:13:45,039
We'll face many things in this life.

192
00:13:45,919 --> 00:13:47,320
Like this lamp in my hand.

193
00:13:48,600 --> 00:13:51,360
See? It flickers and dims,

194
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:54,200
yet it lights the road ahead of us.

195
00:13:57,440 --> 00:13:58,519
Let's face

196
00:13:59,279 --> 00:14:00,480
the darkness behind with courage.

197
00:14:01,559 --> 00:14:02,399
We fear nothing

198
00:14:04,440 --> 00:14:05,720
waiting ahead.

199
00:14:14,460 --> 00:14:16,940
♪A long journey
through mountains and rivers♪

200
00:14:18,020 --> 00:14:20,820
♪Hoping we remain perfectly matched♪

201
00:14:20,820 --> 00:14:27,180
♪Cherish this night. It's not over♪

202
00:14:46,740 --> 00:14:53,740
♪The soul within the dream is started,
and flames consume that soul♪

203
00:14:54,760 --> 00:15:01,100
♪Beyond the dream, a friend leads the horse,
smiling, urging the journey to begin♪

204
00:15:03,190 --> 00:15:06,800
♪Through the turmoil of the martial world,
who is without regret?♪

205
00:15:07,080 --> 00:15:10,860
♪Heaven's will toys with innocence
time and again♪

206
00:15:11,120 --> 00:15:17,790
♪When the fog settles,
who owes the deeper debt?♪

207
00:15:20,940 --> 00:15:25,200
♪Clashing spear tips and flashes of blades
reflect on youthful faces♪

208
00:15:25,410 --> 00:15:28,890
♪Passion masks the sorrow beneath♪

209
00:15:29,160 --> 00:15:33,450
♪Side by side in peril,
life hanging by a thread♪

210
00:15:33,530 --> 00:15:37,200
♪Life and death are easy,
feelings are hard to express♪

211
